OL,3,CBeattie 'no confidence' in Irish
OL,4,CGovernment Troubles legacy role
OL,6,FFormer Ulster Unionist Leader Doug
OL,7,FBeattie says he has has "not one bit"
OL,8,Fof confidence in the Irish
OL,9,FGovernment's dealings over the legacy
OL,10,Fof the Troubles.
OL,12,FHe made the remarks as the Northern
OL,13,FIreland Assembly debated Dublin's role
OL,14,Fin a new legacy framework and the need
OL,15,Ffor the arrangements to attract
OL,16,Fsupport from victims and survivors.
OL,18,FLast week the UK and Irish Governments
OL,19,Fsaid they had reached agreement on how
OL,20,Fkillings from the Northern Ireland
OL,21,FTroubles should be investigated.
