OL,6,FThe new framework includes commitments
OL,7,Fto fundamentally reform the mechanisms
OL,8,Festablished in the 2023 Legacy Act.
OL,10,FThe DUP introduced the motion to the
OL,11,FAssembly on Tuesday, which called for
OL,12,Fthe proposals to be the subject of
OL,13,F"serious and sustained engagement with
OL,14,Finnocent victims, survivors and their
OL,15,Fadvocates".
