OL,6,FIntroducing the motion, DUP MLA Diane
OL,7,FDodds said it was a crucial moment for
OL,8,Fthe Assembly.
OL,10,FShe said: "This Assembly has, once
OL,11,Fagain, the opportunity to stand with
OL,12,Fthe innocent victims of terrorist
OL,13,Fviolence in showing support for it.
OL,15,F"The DUP will always stand with the
OL,16,Finnocent victims of terrorism and we
OL,17,Fare putting on record once again that
OL,18,Fthere can be no viable process on
OL,19,Flegacy which does not have access to
OL,20,Ftruth and justice at its heart.
