OL,6,F"Victims of violence have for many
OL,7,Fyears been sidelined, made to feel
OL,8,Fthey are the pawns of political
OL,9,Fexpediency from successive governments
OL,10,Fwho have served up prisoner releases,
OL,11,Fon-the-run letters of comfort and even
OL,12,Fin this Assembly there are those who
OL,13,Fhave royal pardons in their back
OL,14,Fpockets."
OL,16,FSinn Fein MLA Linda Dillon said
OL,17,FTroubles victims would decide on the
OL,18,Fprocess which meets their needs.
OL,20,FShe said: "The DUP do not get to
